1
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:51,680
What?

2
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,640
Here to turn yourself in?

3
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:57,240
Officer Yao.

4
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,240
I was short-sighted before,

5
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,160
withholding information.

6
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,960
This time, I brought the family.

7
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,960
We will fully cooperate with the investigation.

8
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,220
Do you know each other?

9
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,920
We are neighbors.

10
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,320
Dali is very hardworking and honest.

11
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,520
He could never kill anyone.

12
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,320
You saw it?

13
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,240
At the time,

14
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,760
I happened to see the three of you

15
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,120
facing the rickshaw.

16
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:20,360
There was also a white mist around it.

17
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,160
If you're telling the truth,

18
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:28,200
it doesn't help our investigation at all.

19
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,720
You should take the family home.

20
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,400
We will investigate impartially

21
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,660
and give you an answer.

22
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,530
Officer Yao,

23
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,080
can I see Dali?

24
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,520
Officer, please.

25
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:41,220
No. We haven't finished the interrogation.

26
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,120
Then can I see the body?

27
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,450
Absolutely not.

28
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,039
You're not a coroner.

29
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,280
Then can I see the rickshaw?

30
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,280
The rickshaw?

31
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,380
Why do you want to see that?

32
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,800
The rickshaw isn't the murder weapon, is it?

33
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,479
Besides, it belongs to Dali.

34
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,380
Maybe there are clues on it

35
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,479
that can prove his innocence.

36
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,600
Clues?

37
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,250
Yu Sansheng.

38
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,800
Take her statement.

39
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,800
Verify her family information.

40
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,560
Okay.

41
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,289
Sit here.

42
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:10,940
Come on.

43
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,840
Sit here. Let's go.

44
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,770
Watch your step.

45
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,079
Thank you for your hard work.

46
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:19,680
Excuse me.

47
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,520
Who can tell me where the Director's office is?

48
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,180
Over there.

49
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,340
Thanks. It's nothing.

50
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:26,560
Stop.

51
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,440
What do you want? Just looking for our Director?

52
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:30,920
Well,

53
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:31,730
brother.

54
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,040
Thank you for your hard work, brother.

55
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:33,720
Thank you.

56
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,160
I'm the boss of Wei's Garage.

57
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,320
Man Dali works for me.

58
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,760
I know your Director.

59
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,800
Could you please show me the way?

60
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:44,920
I know him.

61
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,480
Why didn't you say you were an acquaintance earlier?

62
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,360
Come.

63
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,880
Thank you.

64
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,530
Look around,

65
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,460
but don't touch anything inside.

66
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,380
The person was alive at first,

67
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,970
then suddenly died.

68
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,080
Aged instantly.

69
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,440
White-haired blood corpse.

70
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,560
Officer Yao, look.

71
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,340
There are two drops of blood here.

72
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,640
The victim's blood.

73
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,520
It dripped there.

74
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,720
It doesn't look like a drip or splatter.

75
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:39,000
It looks like it was smeared by an index and middle finger.

76
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,220
How do you know?

77
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,440
It's not human blood.

78
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,400
The smell is wrong.

79
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,329
If it's not human blood, what is it?

80
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,530
It's chicken blood.

81
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:56,600
The blood from the seven orifices wasn't human blood.

82
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:59,730
It was applied with fingertips dipped in chicken blood.

83
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,340
When the hand was put down,

84
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,840
the blood on the fingertips

85
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,840
stained the seat.

86
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,480
You mean,

87
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,840
the deceased smeared chicken blood on his face while alive

88
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,770
to look like he was bleeding from his seven orifices?

89
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,960
He was trying to scare Man Dali on purpose.

90
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,040
Does that prove

91
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,060
that Man Dali didn't kill him?

92
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,200
But the man is definitely dead.

93
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,600
The body is in the morgue.

94
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,820
The captain and I examined it.

95
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,520
He didn't die in the car.

96
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,760
Someone moved the body into the car.

97
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,640
Impossible.

98
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:51,000
He was sitting in the car the whole time.

99
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,800
I...

100
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,490
I have the Yin-Yang Eye.

101
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,159
I can see the fragmented souls

102
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,280
