103
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:01,120
Don't give me that supernatural nonsense.

104
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,200
I want solid evidence.

105
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,600
Then ask the forensic doctor

106
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,040
to examine the body first.

107
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:10,040
He definitely didn't die in the car.

108
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,240
Looks like I have to go find her tonight.

109
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,400
I'll let you get back to work.

110
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,490
