115
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,060
Do you have any humanity left?

116
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,560
You have humanity?

117
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,000
Fine.

118
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,659
You have humanity.

119
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,740
You have humanity.

120
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:39,800
You...

121
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,080
Let me tell you,

122
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,940
go get rid of that pregnant woman.

123
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,200
Tell her to watch her mouth

124
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,040
and keep it shut.

125
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,520
You...

126
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,600
What a disgrace.

127
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,159
Boss Lin.

128
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,560
Mrs. Lin,

129
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,320
please save Man Dali.

130
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,200
If anything happens to him,

131
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:58,360
