132
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,000
Please have mercy.

133
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,480
Get up first.

134
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,120
I'll kowtow to you both.

135
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:01,800
No, no, no.

136
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,880
Take care of yourself.

137
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,440
Get up.

138
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,200
Sister-in-law, what are you doing?

139
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,640
Please get up.

140
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,490
I'll go get you a glass of water.

141
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,480
That's exactly why we're here.

142
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:12,600
Sister, don't worry.

143
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,000
The police will definitely ensure justice for Dali.

144
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,000
You should go back and wait for news.

145
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,160
Look,

146
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,700
don't cause trouble for the police here.

147
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,640
Here, take this.

148
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:28,400
Boss Lin,

149
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,960
your car is still with us.

150
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:30,760
We still need to inspect it.

151
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,760
Okay, no problem.

152
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,680
We will cooperate with the investigation.

153
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,010
We'll cooperate fully.

154
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,720
Do you have to take the car apart?

155
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,080
Every car here

156
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,320
