157
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,650
It's their livelihood.

158
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,490
Don't worry.

159
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,720
Once we're done checking,

160
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,800
you can take them back anytime.

161
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,720
Okay. Check whatever you want.

162
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,380
Take these.

163
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,200
Here.

164
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,650
You draw quite well.

165
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,280
Thank you.

166
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,520
Man Dali will clear his name.

167
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,800
So you and the child must stay safe.

168
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,440
Take care.

169
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,680
I've arranged a car to take you home.

170
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,880
We'll find a way to help Dali.

171
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,700
Get me a car.

172
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,480
I'm going to Xianlesi. Okay.

173
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,680
Over there. Car number 2 is free.

174
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,820
I'll drive you.

175
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,640
No need. You take the family home.

176
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,970
Are you going to see the medical examiner?

177
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,160
None of your business.

178
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,840
Let's go.

179
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:17,960
Come on.

180
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:18,440
Hey.

181
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,320
The car is over there.

182
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,450
I'll walk you there.

183
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:22,560
Watch out.

184
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,600
There are steps.

185
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,400
Be careful.

186
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,160
Sister,

187
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,920
aren't you afraid of getting into trouble?

188
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,180
If it were anyone else,

189
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,160
even if they were there,

190
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,760
they wouldn't get involved.

191
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,760
Leaving aside that Sister Juan treats me well,

192
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,580
even if it were a stranger,

193
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,320
I wouldn't want them to be wrongly accused.

194
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,290
You're amazing.

195
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:44,760
It's nothing.

196
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:45,760
In times like these,

197
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,800
we women have to look out for each other

198
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,330
to survive these hard days.

199
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,250
Look out for each other.

200
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,200
You really are a good person.

201
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,480
Sister,

202
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:02,520
could you send a rickshaw for me?

203
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,770
Where are you going?

204
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:08,400
A place called Xianlesi.

205
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,880
Xianlesi?

206
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,520
I'll send a car to take you there.

207
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,800
Sister,

208
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,640
you're a good person too.

209
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,679
I.

210
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,600
I want.

211
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,400
I want you.

212
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,200
I want your...

213
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,400
I want your love.

214
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:47,160
Why don't you come over?

215
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,640
I.

216
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,160
I want.

217
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,080
I want you.

218
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,960
I want your...

219
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:00,120
I want your love.

220
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,840
Why don't you say it?

221
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,370
What are you doing here?

222
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,290
I'm here to help you solve the case.

223
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,080
Don't cause trouble.

224
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,120
This isn't your business.

225
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,720
Go.

226
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,720
Wenxuan,

227
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,460
don't leave me here alone.

228
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:15,680
Sorry.

229
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,840
I forgot you're not suited for this occasion.

230
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,900
My mom made me come here to socialize.

231
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,440
All right.

232
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,320
May I have this dance?

233
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,520
Just like at our prom.

234
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,040
I found a new lead.

235
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,480
It will definitely help you.

236
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,080
What lead?

237
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,960
We need an autopsy first.

238
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,280
Where is the forensic doctor?

239
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,140
Male or female?

240
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,040
I...

241
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,600
I want...

242
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:41,520
I want you...

243
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,920
I want you to tell me.

244
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,400
You came in such a hurry.

245
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,420
Are you rushing for a date?

246
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,120
Why won't you...

247
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,400
Why won't you...

248
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:54,080
Why won't you tell me?

249
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:00,760
Thank you.

250
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,440
Great!

251
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,360
Good!

252
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,520
Thank you, everyone.

253
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,040
Thank you.

254
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,280
Great!

255
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,360
Really good!

256
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,560
Great! Sounds great!

257
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,320
Sounds great! Wonderful!

258
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,080
