267
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:17,360
Miss Jasmine!

268
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:17,760
So beautiful!

269
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:18,280
Miss Jasmine,

270
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,010
