271
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,880
Miss Jasmine!

272
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,480
It's mine!

273
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,280
This is mine!

274
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:21,640
