278
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,360
I'm so happy!

279
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,960
Come on, let's dance.

280
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,200
No. I'm here to...

281
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,760
